### Get all blogs (with user population)
GET http://localhost:3003/api/blogs

### Add a new blog (requires valid token)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.TOKEN_WILL_BE_REPLACED_AFTER_LOGIN

{
  "title": "Blog Post with JWT Auth",
  "author": "Authenticated User",
  "url": "https://example.com/jwt-auth",
  "likes": 3
}

### Add blog without token (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Blog Without Token",
  "author": "Anonymous",
  "url": "https://example.com/no-token"
}

### Add blog with invalid token (should fail)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/blogs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token

{
  "title": "Blog with Invalid Token",
  "author": "Hacker",
  "url": "https://example.com/invalid-token"
}
